samplers on the market, and all you have to do is plug
them in to your computer, grab sound samples off CD,
cassette or radio and use them. Unfortunately there are
two problems in enjoying these sources of superb sound:
firstly sampler cartridges are rather expensive, secondly
stealing someone else's audio creations is illegal! No
